    rdfs:comment "Distance in miles from the Property to a nearby facility (school / health-care / transport). xsd:decimal. Domain opda:NearbyFacility (the proximity relation on the genus), reused across the amenity bands; flat per §Q6a."@en ;
    dct:source <https://w3id.org/opda/data-dictionary#propertyPack.nearbyFacilities.healthCare[].distanceInMiles>, <https://w3id.org/opda/data-dictionary#propertyPack.nearbyFacilities.schools[].distanceInMiles>, <https://w3id.org/opda/data-dictionary#propertyPack.nearbyFacilities.transport[].distanceInMiles> ;
